Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.99,0:06:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.70,0:06:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一起做嘛 模仿海獺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.57,0:06:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.93,0:06:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前和家人一起去水族館的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.49,0:06:49.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一回到家 小冠就「海獺 海獺」地說個沒完
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.25,0:06:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還把橙子放在肚子上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.20,0:06:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那都是小時候的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.88,0:06:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候真開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.51,0:06:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 晶馬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.58,0:07:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你模仿的海馬 也是一絕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.46,0:07:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海馬 海馬 海馬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.85,0:07:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 企鵝泳游得好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.79,0:07:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不過在陸地上就有點呆呆的了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.50,0:07:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被晶馬這麼說 企鵝可會跟你急啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.59,0:07:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這算什麼話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.83,0:07:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我接個電話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.44,0:07:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是女孩子?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.90,0:07:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你適可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.13,0:07:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的 我會處理好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.86,0:07:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.47,0:07:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺我都要被一群「花花公子冠葉菌」給傳染了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.91,0:07:50.95,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.35,0:07:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看 企鵝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.36,0:07:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 不要這麼大聲說話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.37,0:07:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,企鵝又不會跑掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.46,0:07:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.01,0:08:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 企鵝先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.46,0:08:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.58,0:08:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.61,0:08:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽毬 我們去買紀念品吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.28,0:08:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天只要是陽毬喜歡的 我都可以買來送你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.43,0:08:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.64,0:08:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 因為今天是陽毬日呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.60,0:08:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.05,0:08:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 是錯覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.81,0:08:27.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這個好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.71,0:08:30.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個海獺感覺跟真的一樣 好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.82,0:08:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是海獺的話 已經有小冠了就算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.42,0:08:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在家裏讓他模仿就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.08,0:08:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在他還會模仿嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.74,0:08:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會模仿的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.41,0:08:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為今天是陽毬日嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.22,0:08:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小晶呢 就模仿海馬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.57,0:08:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要模仿嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.55,0:08:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.28,0:08:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 今天我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.40,0:08:55.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王大人~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.60,0:08:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.39,0:08:58.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽毬…這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.24,0:08:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.33,0:09:00.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噁心得好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.28,0:09:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.46,0:09:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絲帶要什麼顏色的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.56,0:09:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…要粉色的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.59,0:09:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.98,0:09:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.71,0:09:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裏啊 我找了半天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.53,0:09:15.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是老哥太慢了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.74,0:09:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那陽毬呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.54,0:09:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.37,0:09:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼不好好看著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.57,0:09:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到剛才我們都在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.25,0:09:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 誰叫下救護車
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.34,0:09:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個女孩子在廣場上暈倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.49,0:09:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快叫救護車
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.02,0:09:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽毬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.59,0:09:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽毬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.59,0:09:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽毬!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.95,0:09:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注射一瓶腎上腺素 一單位阿托品…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.25,0:09:56.34,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}高倉小姐? 高倉陽毬小姐!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.67,0:10:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小冠 小晶…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.75,0:10:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永別了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.98,0:10:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽毬…為什麼這麼突然就…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.95,0:10:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個醫生 看來也不一定就是庸醫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.51,0:10:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說能活下來才是奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.88,0:10:40.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我們做好隨時可能會來的準備
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.80,0:10:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.05,0:10:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽毬的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.73,0:10:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有痛苦 而且還去了回憶中的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.94,0:10:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如說是幸福的結局
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.24,0:10:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 我們先聯繫池部叔叔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.49,0:10:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有各種各樣的手續 我們也辦不了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.64,0:11:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你個混蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.56,0:11:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然敢對自己的妹妹…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.71,0:11:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的妹妹說出這麼冷淡的話!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.14,0:11:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是接受了事實而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.89,0:11:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.23,0:11:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會是陽毬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.98,0:11:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只是一個 光和家人一起吃飯就會說幸福的女孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.90,0:11:23.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.63,0:11:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.72,0:11:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是對我們的懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.44,0:11:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生存 戰略!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.57,0:11:39.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.35,0:11:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼…怎麼回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.00,0:11:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從通往你等命運之地而來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.94,0:11:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慶幸吧 我決定把這女孩的餘生再略微延長下去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.90,0:12:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果 想讓這女孩一直保持復活狀態…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.02,0:12:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.85,0:12:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小晶?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.03,0:12:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小冠?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.46,0:12:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏…是哪裏呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.97,0:12:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底是怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.65,0:12:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽毬!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.13,0:12:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 陽毬還活著!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.04,0:12:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.10,0:12:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了小晶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.63,0:12:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 你哭了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.61,0:12:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太大驚小怪啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.44,0:12:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.50,0:12:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很奇怪是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.00,0:12:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶吶 我到底是怎麼啦?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.02,0:12:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是醫院嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.05,0:12:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 得去告訴鷲塚醫生一聲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.76,0:12:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微等我一下 我馬上就回來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.78,0:12:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小晶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.62,0:12:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.98,0:13:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開吃咯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.18,0:13:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真的哎 這個煎雞蛋好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.96,0:13:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 小晶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.31,0:13:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次也教我做這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.76,0:13:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 這點事什麼時候都行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.07,0:13:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的味噌湯也很不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.12,0:13:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今往後我也要一起分擔家事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小晶一個人太辛苦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.56,0:13:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有在做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.13,0:13:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥你不過是打掃打掃浴室而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.03,0:13:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一碗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.10,0:13:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃這麼多不要緊嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.57,0:13:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 完全沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.00,0:13:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫生也說能做的事就多做些
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.02,0:13:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過幾天能不能回學校呢~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.30,0:13:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.55,0:13:43.27,flashback_br,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fad(300,0)}東鷗醫院 診室
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.09,0:13:40.89,flashback_red,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,200)}鷲塚醫生很震驚。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.90,0:13:43.27,flashback_red,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}他目睹了自己從醫經歷中最為驚奇的一幕。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.73,0:13:45.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.86,0:13:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然能從當時的狀況恢復到現在這種程度
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.89,0:13:52.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且情況還很穩定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.79,0:13:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這簡直可以說…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.25,0:13:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.73,0:14:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.24,0:14:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼大清早的竟然有快遞來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.80,0:14:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰寄來的?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.50,0:14:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄件信息也沒寫…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.97,0:14:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫「冷凍運輸」的 難道這是生鮮食品?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.06,0:14:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.91,0:14:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是茄子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.00,0:14:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是這麼說 不覺得太大了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.46,0:14:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還凍起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.81,0:14:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶馬 看時間…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.45,0:14:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.69,0:14:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 陽毬就拜託你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.29,0:14:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出門啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.98,0:14:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匆匆忙忙的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.59,0:14:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 這玩意兒要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.30,0:14:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也塞不進冰箱的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.22,0:14:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 我原以為這不過是走運
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.43,0:14:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為又不講理又殘酷的神明 出於一時高興
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.82,0:14:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便為我們的命運帶來了奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.60,0:15:03.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者是因為即使連我們這種人 也有幸福的權利
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.64,0:15:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 高倉家弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.73,0:15:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去喝個下午茶不~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.22,0:15:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我發現了一個超可愛的女孩在那打工
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.17,0:15:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我今天得趕緊回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.02,0:15:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太無情啦~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.65,0:15:20.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別趴上來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.41,0:15:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個露肚臍的女孩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.83,0:15:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你老哥的話一定會跟我去的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.59,0:15:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別把我跟冠葉劃等號!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.38,0:15:31.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是櫻花女高的!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.92,0:15:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到沒 中間那個女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.05,0:15:33.37,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}那是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.37,0:15:35.40,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}不知道 男人嘛男人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.21,0:15:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她真是相當…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.93,0:15:37.67,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}那還是無視吧 無視掉無視掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.69,0:15:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦回過頭來了 在看這裏!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.36,0:15:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧 莫非在看我?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.03,0:15:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上幾年級呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.48,0:15:42.38,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}吶 去喝下午茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.45,0:15:43.79,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}好啊 去哪家?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.35,0:15:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邊上那個短髮的也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.12,0:15:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也這麼覺得吧 高倉家弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.66,0:15:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 定期車票不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.86,0:15:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 糟了 上體育課換衣服的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.07,0:16:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放更衣櫃裏了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.74,0:16:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,企鵝?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.74,0:16:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的定期車票…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.80,0:16:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.89,0:16:14.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不見了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賣完了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.58,0:16:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來晚了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.93,0:16:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好貴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.56,0:16:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.53,0:16:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傘?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.62,0:16:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我的?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.82,0:16:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我冒昧地問一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.25,0:16:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這企鵝是什麼情況?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.31,0:16:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 那個哥哥在說什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.77,0:16:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噓 別多看 趕緊過來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.08,0:17:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別人還看不見…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.13,0:17:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.16,0:17:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.94,0:17:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼 還是淋濕了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.43,0:17:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有件詭異的事情啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.35,0:17:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓它帶傘去了 沒遇上嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.30,0:17:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「沒遇上」?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.19,0:17:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.29,0:17:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.57,0:17:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 在那地方把線穿過去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.72,0:18:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底…是啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.65,0:18:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這什麼情況啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.15,0:18:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就如你所見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.85,0:18:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那個快遞解凍以後就是這群小傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.44,0:18:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像還聽得懂我們說話 至少能幫忙跑個腿啥的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.61,0:18:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.39,0:18:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不對! 這也太奇怪了吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.74,0:18:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 這群傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.42,0:18:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 除我們以外的人都看不見它們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.33,0:18:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生存戰略!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.40,0:19:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Imagine——
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.47,0:19:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告知你等必將一事無成之人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.54,0:19:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 啥? 啥?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.14,0:19:35.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們要得到企鵝罐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.14,0:19:35.16,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(746,660)}Penguin Drum
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.44,0:19:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼呀 陽毬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.71,0:19:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並非你等的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.11,0:19:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從你等的命運所至之地而來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.58,0:19:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.66,0:19:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那帽子在操縱陽毬!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.98,0:19:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧… 那不是在水族館買的玩具嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.15,0:19:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這女孩現因我的神力得以暫續生命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.26,0:20:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而天下沒有免費的午餐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.24,0:20:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要收下這條命的代價
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.72,0:20:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 代價什麼的不奇怪嗎——
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.41,0:20:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來進行生存戰略吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.40,0:20:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人是為何而生的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.36,0:20:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若創造人類的目的 是只為讓其度過忙碌一生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.02,0:20:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那究竟是一種懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.35,0:20:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是一個諷刺的玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.92,0:20:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若真是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.16,0:20:58.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忠於基因內編寫好的生存戰略而生活的動物 反而更加簡單和美好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.75,0:21:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這世上真有神明 我只想問他一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.13,0:21:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在人世間 真的存在「命運」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.92,0:21:15.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽毬 不行啦 快點醒過來…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.35,0:21:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被操縱了啦 帽子把你整個人變掉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.33,0:21:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果人類無視命運
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.42,0:21:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無視本能和基因的命令 而愛上了某個人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.61,0:21:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神啊 那他…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.76,0:21:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還能被稱為人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.74,0:21:40.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.93,0:21:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 討厭「命運」這個詞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.63,0:21:54.63,title_no,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs42}1{\fs30\pos(640,630)}ST STATION
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.63,0:21:54.63,title_text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運之鐘鳴響
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.66,0:23:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡「命運」這個詞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.69,0:23:31.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有任何一件事是無意義的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.24,0:23:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信著命運
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.41,0:23:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來進行生存戰略吧
